sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as ลูกค้า
    participant UI as machine-ui
    participant BC as BuyController
    participant Om as Omise
    participant WH as POST /api/buy/omise-webhook
    participant Inv as InventoryService
    participant Agent as Agent / SIO

    User->>UI: เลือก QR / PromptPay
    UI->>BC: POST /api/buy/checkout
    BC->>Om: create_charge (pending)
    Om-->>BC: pending + QR URI
    BC->>BC: pending_orders[charge_id] in memory
    BC-->>UI: pending_payment + qr_code
    User->>Om: สแกนจ่าย
    Om->>WH: POST charge.complete (optional HMAC)
    WH->>WH: _verify_webhook_signature
    WH->>Om: Charge.retrieve (recovery metadata)
    WH->>BC: _execute_dispense(charge_id)
    BC->>Inv: deduct_stock + update status paid
    BC->>Agent: HTTP or Socket.IO dispatch
    WH-->>Om: 200 JSON
    Note over UI,BC: UI อาจ poll GET /api/buy/status/:charge_id ควบคู่
